column5: Click here for game  Click here for the show's web site  We enjoy the show at our house, I'm sure there are a few on OFC that like it too.  The game is a time waster, but what the hey? I got called a jackass everytime!

Wow, do the pumps go fast in round 2.  I blew up 4 cars in a row and the game ended.  I have a feeeling that I will try again later this aft... I, too, was deemed a jackass.  Corner Gas is one of the funniest shows in a long time!
I got hired.....but gas pumps don't pay enough so I quit!....LOL
LOL, not a job for me, by the time I walk to the pumps the stations closed. People did mention I was number 1!
I just put up a self serve sign - and raised the prices! Ya - I was deemed a jackass also!   Don
